    {
        "name": "run_command",
        "description": "Execute a shell command. 1.20 HARDENED PROTOCOL: 1. ALWAYS wrap in 'timeout <SECONDS>'. 2. Use 'WaitMsBeforeAsync: 10000' to force sync capture during IPC flood. 3. If a command hangs, immediately use send_command_input with Terminate: true.",
